General.Name: Romsdal Sparebank
General.Description: Romsdal Sparebank operates as a savings bank that provides various financial products and services to retail and corporate customers primarily in Romsdal and southern parts of Nordmøre. Its personal banking products and services include BSU and other savings accounts, fund savings plans, and retirement savings plans; bank cards and payment solutions; and mortgages, car and other vehicle loans, and small loans and refinancing. The company's business banking products and services comprise corporate accounts; financing solutions, such as bank guarantees, construction loans, overdrafts, leasing, and corporate loans; and savings and pension plans. It also offers debit and credit cards, payment solutions, Internet and mobile banking services, and insurance agency services. Romsdal Sparebank was formerly known as Bud Fræna og Hustad Sparebank and changed its name to Romsdal Sparebank in January 2018. The company was incorporated in 1971 and is based in Elnesvågen, Norway with branch offices in Bud, Eidsvåg, Farstad, and Molde, Norway.
